{"sn1.32:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 1.32 ","sn1.32:0.2":"4. Satullapakayikavagga ","sn1.32:0.3":"Maccharisutta ","sn1.32:1.1":"Ekam samayam bhagava savatthiyam viharati jetavane anathapindikassa arame. ","sn1.32:1.2":"Atha kho sambahula satullapakayika devatayo abhikkantaya rattiya abhikkantavanna kevalakappam jetavanam obhasetva yena bhagava tenupasankamimsu; upasankamitva bhagavantam abhivadetva ekamantam atthamsu. ","sn1.32:1.3":"Ekamantam thita kho eka devata bhagavato santike imam gatham abhasi: ","sn1.32:2.1":"“Macchera ca pamada ca, ","sn1.32:2.2":"evam danam na diyati; ","sn1.32:2.3":"Punnam akankhamanena, ","sn1.32:2.4":"deyyam hoti vijanata”ti. ","sn1.32:3.1":"Atha kho apara devata bhagavato santike ima gathayo abhasi: ","sn1.32:4.1":"“Yasseva bhito na dadati macchari, ","sn1.32:4.2":"Tadevadadato bhayam; ","sn1.32:4.3":"Jighaccha ca pipasa ca, ","sn1.32:4.4":"Yassa bhayati macchari; ","sn1.32:4.5":"Tameva balam phusati, ","sn1.32:4.6":"Asmim loke paramhi ca. ","sn1.32:5.1":"Tasma vineyya maccheram, ","sn1.32:5.2":"dajja danam malabhibhu; ","sn1.32:5.3":"Punnani paralokasmim, ","sn1.32:5.4":"patittha honti paninan”ti. ","sn1.32:6.1":"Atha kho apara devata bhagavato santike ima gathayo abhasi: ","sn1.32:7.1":"“Te matesu na miyanti, ","sn1.32:7.2":"panthanamva sahabbajam; ","sn1.32:7.3":"Appasmim ye pavecchanti, ","sn1.32:7.4":"esa dhammo sanantano. ","sn1.32:8.1":"Appasmeke pavecchanti, ","sn1.32:8.2":"bahuneke na dicchare; ","sn1.32:8.3":"Appasma dakkhina dinna, ","sn1.32:8.4":"sahassena samam mita”ti. ","sn1.32:9.1":"Atha kho apara devata bhagavato santike ima gathayo abhasi: ","sn1.32:10.1":"“Duddadam dadamananam, ","sn1.32:10.2":"dukkaram kamma kubbatam; ","sn1.32:10.3":"Asanto nanukubbanti, ","sn1.32:10.4":"satam dhammo duranvayo. ","sn1.32:11.1":"Tasma satanca asatam, ","sn1.32:11.2":"nana hoti ito gati; ","sn1.32:11.3":"Asanto nirayam yanti, ","sn1.32:11.4":"santo saggaparayana”ti. ","sn1.32:12.1":"Atha kho apara devata bhagavato santike etadavoca: ","sn1.32:12.2":"“kassa nu kho, bhagava, subhasitan”ti? ","sn1.32:13.1":"“Sabbasam vo subhasitam pariyayena; api ca mamapi sunatha—","sn1.32:14.1":"Dhammam care yopi samunjakam care, ","sn1.32:14.2":"Daranca posam dadamappakasmim; ","sn1.32:14.3":"Satam sahassanam sahassayaginam, ","sn1.32:14.4":"Kalampi nagghanti tathavidhassa te”ti. ","sn1.32:15.1":"Atha kho apara devata bhagavantam gathaya ajjhabhasi: ","sn1.32:16.1":"“Kenesa yanno vipulo mahaggato, ","sn1.32:16.2":"Samena dinnassa na agghameti; ","sn1.32:16.3":"Katham satam sahassanam sahassayaginam, ","sn1.32:16.4":"Kalampi nagghanti tathavidhassa te”ti. ","sn1.32:17.1":"“Dadanti heke visame nivittha, ","sn1.32:17.2":"Chetva vadhitva atha socayitva; ","sn1.32:17.3":"Sa dakkhina assumukha sadanda, ","sn1.32:17.4":"Samena dinnassa na agghameti. ","sn1.32:18.1":"Evam satam sahassanam sahassayaginam, ","sn1.32:18.2":"Kalampi nagghanti tathavidhassa te”ti. "}